              "reasoning": "The user is asking if I've created the frontend pages for Kelola Produk and Kelola Kategori with full CRUD support. Looking back, I created placeholder pages earlier but they weren't connected to the backend API. Now that the backend is ready, I need to:\n\n1. Update the Kelola Kategori page with full CRUD (create, read, update, delete)\n2. Update the Kelola Produk page with full CRUD including image upload\n\nLet me create proper frontend pages with:\n- API integration\n- Create/Edit modals\n- Delete confirmation\n- Loading states\n- Toast notifications",
