              "reasoning": "Done! I've reverted the product listing from card grid to table layout while keeping the modern styling:\n\n- Header with Package icon\n- Full width searchbar\n- Filter section\n- Table layout with:\n  - Product thumbnail + name + description\n  - Category badge\n  - Price\n  - Stock (red if 0)\n  - Status badge (Aktif/Nonaktif)\n  - Actions dropdown (Edit, Hapus)\n- Modern modals for create/edit and delete confirmation",
