            {
              "type": "reasoning",
              "is_native": true,
              "reasoning": "The user wants:\n1. Below 'Kelola Produk' - just a short description instead of stats like \"1 produk • 1 aktif • 0 habis\"\n2. Filter dropdown on the right side of the searchbar (same line)\n3. Make the page more compact like the sidebar\n\nLet me update the Kelola Produk page with these changes.",
