              "reasoning": "Now I need to add pagination. Let me update the component:\n1. Add `currentPage` state\n2. Calculate `totalPages` based on filtered products\n3. Slice the filtered products based on current page\n4. Always show table header and pagination\n5. Show empty rows or message when no data",
