              "type": "reasoning",
              "is_native": true,
              "reasoning": "Done! I added:\n1. Pagination with max 10 items per page\n2. Table header always visible (even with no products)\n3. Pagination always visible at bottom of table\n4. Empty state now shows inside the table body instead of replacing the whole table\n5. Reset to page 1 when filters change\n6. Shows \"1-10 dari 25 produk\" style info",
              "signature": ""
