            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Done! Added pagination with:\n\n### Features:\n- **Max 10 per page** - `ITEMS_PER_PAGE = 10`\n- **Table header always visible** - Even when no products\n- **Pagination always visible** - Shows at bottom of table\n- **Page info** - \"1-10 dari 25 produk\" or \"0 produk\"\n- **Page buttons** - Prev/Next arrows + numbered pages\n- **Active page** - Black background\n- **Auto reset to page 1** - When filters/search change\n\n### UI:\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ Produk │ Kategori │ Harga │ Stok │ Status │ │\n├─────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│ (empty state or product rows)               │\n├─────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│ 1-10 dari 25 produk    [<] [1] [2] [3] [>] │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```",
