          "content": [
            {
              "type": "reasoning",
              "is_native": true,
              "reasoning": "Looking at the sidebar:\n- Search button: `h-9`, `text-sm`, icon `h-4 w-4`\n- Menu items: `text-sm font-medium`, `py-1.5 px-2`, icon `h-4 w-4`\n- Section labels: `text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase`\n\nThe Kelola Produk page is currently using smaller sizes like `text-xs`, `h-8` buttons. Let me update it to match the sidebar better:\n- Buttons: `h-9` instead of `h-8`\n- Text: `text-sm` instead of `text-xs` for most things\n- Keep consistency with the sidebar styling",
