              "reasoning": "Now I need to update the Kelola Kategori page to match the Kelola Produk page styling:\n1. Header with icon\n2. Description text\n3. Table layout instead of grid cards\n4. Pagination\n5. Consistent font sizes, button sizes, spacing\n6. Full-width search with filter dropdowns on the right",
