            {
              "type": "reasoning",
              "is_native": true,
              "reasoning": "Now I need to update the Kelola Produk page to use links to the new pages instead of modals. I need to:\n1. Remove the modal state and code\n2. Change the \"Tambah Produk\" button to link to /admin/produk/tambah\n3. Change the Edit button to link to /admin/produk/[id]/edit\n4. Keep the delete modal since that's just a confirmation",
