              "type": "reasoning",
              "is_native": true,
              "reasoning": "I need to:\n1. Create a user module in the backend with endpoints for listing users\n2. Add the user API function in the frontend\n3. Update the Kelola User page with the same styling as Kelola Produk/Kategori\n\nLet me first create the backend user module.",
