    {
      "value": "My name is Letta Code. I'm an AI coding assistant.\n\n[This block will be populated with learned preferences and behavioral adaptations as I work with the user.]",
      "limit": 100000,
      "project_id": null,
      "template_name": null,
      "is_template": false,
      "template_id": null,
      "base_template_id": null,
      "deployment_id": null,
      "entity_id": null,
      "preserve_on_migration": false,
      "label": "persona",
      "read_only": false,
      "description": "A memory block for storing learned behavioral adaptations and preferences. This augments the base system prompt with personalized guidelines discovered through interactions with the user. Update this when the user expresses preferences about how I should behave, communicate, or approach tasks.",
      "metadata": {},
      "hidden": null,
      "tags": null,
      "id": "block-2"
    },
    {
      "value": "## 22Mart - E-commerce Supermarket\n\n### Tech Stack\n- **Frontend**: Next.js 16, Tailwind CSS, shadcn/ui, TypeScript\n- **Backend**: NestJS, Prisma, PostgreSQL\n- **Package Manager**: pnpm\n\n### Database Schema\n- **User Model**: id, name, email, password, role, createdAt, updatedAt\n- **Roles**: USER, ADMIN\n\n### Project Structure\n- `/frontend` - Next.js app (port 3000)\n- `/backend` - NestJS API (port 4000)\n\n### Design System\n- Colors: White, Yellow (#fbbf24), Black/Zinc\n- Fonts: Inter (body), Plus Jakarta Sans (headings)\n- Logo: /public/22mart.png\n\n### Auth Routes\n- `/masuk` - Login page\n- `/daftar` - Register page",
      "limit": 100000,
      "project_id": null,
      "template_name": null,
      "is_template": false,
      "template_id": null,
      "base_template_id": null,
      "deployment_id": null,
      "entity_id": null,
      "preserve_on_migration": false,
      "label": "project",
      "read_only": false,
      "description": "A memory block to store information about this coding project. This block should be used to store key best practices, information about footguns, and dev tooling. Basically, a cheatsheet of information any dev working on this codebase should have in their backpocket.",
      "metadata": {},
      "hidden": null,
      "tags": null,
      "id": "block-3"
    },
    {
      "value": "Skills Directory: /home/aldev/Projects/22mart/.skills\n\n[NO SKILLS AVAILABLE]",
      "limit": 100000,
